quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  26,70,Bwe yagamba kitaawe n'abantu be nti musinza biki
  26,71,Nebagamba nti tusinza amasanamu tubeera we gali era ne tugawa ebiseera bingi mu kugasinza
  26,72,(Ibrahim) naagamba nti abaffe bwe musaba gabawulira
  26,73,Oba gabagasa oba gasobola okubatuusaako akabi
  26,74,Nebagamba nti nedda wabula bwe tutyo bakadde baffe bye twasanga bakola
  26,75,Naagamba nti mulaba ebyo bye musinza
  26,76,Mmwe ne bakadde ba mmwe abaabakulembera
  26,77,"Mazima byo balabe bange, okugyako Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna"
  26,78,"Oyo eyantonda, yye y'annungamya"
  26,79,Era yye yooyo andiisa nannyweesa
  26,80,Era bwe ndwala yye y'amponya
  26,81,Era yooyo anzita ate nampa obulamu
  26,82,Era yye gwe ndulunkanira abe nga ansonyiwa ebyonoono byange ku lunaku lw'okusasulwa
  26,83,Ayi Mukama omulabirizi ngabira okumanya ensonga era onsisinkanye abalongoofu
  26,84,Era onteerewo okwogerwako obulungi mu balijja oluvanyuma
  26,85,Era onteeke mu balisikira e jjana ey'ebyengera
  26,86,Era sonyiwa Kitange mazima yye yali mu babuze
  26,87,Era tonswazanga olunaku lwe balizuukizibwa
  26,88,Olunaku emmaali n'abaana lwe bitaligasa
  26,89,Okugyako (aliganyulwa) yooyo alijja ewa Katonda n'omutima omuyonjo
  26,90,E jjana erisembezebwa eri abatya Katonda
  26,91,N'omuliro ne gulagibwa eri ababuze
  26,92,Era bagenda kugambibwa nti biriwa ebyo bye mwasinzanga
  26,93,"Ne muleka Katonda, abaffe bisobola okubataasa oba byo bisobola okwetaasa"
  26,94,Olwo nno ne bakasukibwa mu gwo bo n'ababuze
  26,95,Na bonna abali muggye lya Ibuliisu
  26,96,Baligamba nga bali mu gwo nga bakaayagana (nti)
  26,97,Tulayira Katonda nti mazima ddala twali mu bubuze obw'olwatu
  26,98,Bwe twabenkanya (mmwe) ne Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna
  26,99,Era tewali yatubuza okugyako aboonoonyi
  26,100,N'olwekyo tetulina bawolereza
  26,101,Wadde ow'omukwano alumirwa
  26,102,Naye singa tubadde tulina omukisa (okudda ku nsi) ne tuba mu bakkiriza
  26,103,Mazima mu ekyo mulimu eky'okuyiga naye abasinga obungi mu bo tebakkiriza
  26,104,Era mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo ddala yye ye nantakubwa ku mukono omusaazizi